<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/warehouseDetail.css"/>
  <title>창고 상세 정보</title>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
  </header>
  <div class="photo-container test-gray">
    photos
  </div>

  <!--창고 상세정보 타이틀-->
  <div id="title-container" class="container">
    <p>
      <span class="badge-text-purple">
        <img src="/image/icon/map_mark_icon.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 
        대구광역시 북구 산격동 112-22
      </span>
      <span class="badge-text">
        <img src="/image/icon/verified_icon.svg" style="width:30px; height:30px; background: no-repeat;"/>
        인증창고
      </span>
    </p>
    <h3 class="wh-detail-title">대구 광역시 글로벌 물류센터</h3>
    <p class="badge-text">
      <img src="/image/icon/phone-alt-solid.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 053-1234-1234
      <img src="/image/icon/envelope-solid.svg" class="badge-svg"/> daegu@gmail.com
    </p>
  </div>
  <!--창고 상세정보 타이틀-->
  
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-start">
      <!--창고 정보 테이블-->
      <div id="wh-info-table" class="col">
        <h3 class="wh-detail-title">창고정보</h3>
        <p class="badge-text">
          <img src="/image/icon/truck-solid.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 도킹시설
          <img src="/image/icon/is_racked_icon.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 파레트 렉
          <img src="/image/icon/elevator_icon.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 엘리베이터
          <img src="/image/icon/is_bonded_icon.svg" class="badge-svg"/> 보세
        </p>
        <table class="table info-table">
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>창고명</td>
            <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3">대구 광역시 글로벌 물류센터</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>종류</td>
            <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3">일반 창고</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>임대료</td>
            <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3" style="color: #D00101; font-family:'nanum-b'">평당 ￦800 /일</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>주소</td>
            <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3">대구 광역시 북구 산격동 112-13</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>상세주소</td>
            <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3">대구 스마트 물류단지 내부</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>대지면적</td>
            <td class="info-table-td">9000㎡ (2722평)</td>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>연면적</td>
            <td class="info-table-td">8900㎡ (2692평)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>공용면적</td>
            <td class="info-table-td">2900㎡ (877평)</td>
            <td class=info-table-td-head>전용면적</td>
            <td class="info-table-td">6000㎡ (1815평)</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      <!--창고 정보 테이블-->

      <!--견적 확인 카드뷰-->
      <div class="col-5">
        <form>
          <div class="info-card" id="contract-card" >
            <div class="card-body">
              <div>
                <span id="wh-detail-contract-card-title">합계</span>
                <span id="wh-detail-contract-card-price">670,000 ￦</span>
              </div>
              
              <div class="contract-card-element">
                <p>임대기간 선택</p>
                <input id="info-card-start-date" type="date" class="input-contract-info"/>
                <img id="info-card-arrow" src="/image/icon/arrow-right-solid.svg"/>
                <input id="info-card-end-date" type="date" class="input-contract-info"/>
              </div>

              <div class="contract-card-element" >
                <div style="margin-left: 9%;">
                  <p>최대 700평</p>
                  <span style="text-align:center;">
                    <input id="info-card-area-for-contract" type="number" placeholder="임대면적" class="input-contract-info" min="0"/>
                    <span style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-family: 'nanum-b'; color: gray; float:inline-end;">평</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="contract-card-element" style="text-align:center;">
                <button id="contract-submit" type="submit" class="btn btn-main">견적확인</button>
                <p class="submit-footer">입력 정보를 모두 채운 후 견적을 확인해주세요.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <!--견적 확인 카드뷰-->
    </div>

    <!--창고 상세정보-->
    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <h3 class="wh-detail-title">상세정보</h3>
      <table class="table info-table">
        <tr>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>층수</td>
          <td class="info-table-td">1층</td>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>유효층고</td>
          <td class="info-table-td">약 11m</td>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>출입가능차량</td>
          <td class="info-table-td">전차종 출입가능</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>준공일</td>
          <td class="info-table-td">2021.08.28</td>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>접근성</td>
          <td class="info-table-td" colspan="3">정왕IC 9km, 남안산IC 10km </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>창고소개</td>
          <td class="info-table-td" colspan="6">깔끔한 신축 물류 창고 입니다.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class=info-table-td-head>보유장비현황 및 특이사항</td>
          <td class="info-table-td" colspan="6">
              □ 물류장비
              - 지게차 5대 : 전동 5대
              파렛트
              - 목재 : 단면 양방향 1000ea(1000＊1200),
              □ 보안설비
              - 보안시스템 완비(출입보안, CCTV 등)
              □ 화재설비
              - 소화기, 소화전, 화재경보기, 화재감지기, 가스누설경보기, 피난기구, 스프링쿨러 등
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
    <!--창고 상세정보-->
    <div style="margin-top:3rem; margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <h3 class="wh-detail-title">창고환경</h3>
      <div class="info-card" style="height: 600px;">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <%- include('footer') %>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
